 The words in angle brackets are taken from <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Stanislaus Murray Hamilton, ed. &lt;i&gt;Letters to Washington and Accompanying Papers&lt;/i&gt;. 5 vols. Boston and New York, 18981902. ]">Hamilton, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Letters to Washington</span></span>, 4:23537.</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-09-02-0198-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-09-02-0198-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-09-02-0183" class="document">Edward Charlton to GW, 19 June</a>. See also <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-09-02-0183&amp;expandNote=GEWN-02-09-02-0183-fn-0001#GEWN-02-09-02-0183-fn-0001" class="document">note 1 of that document</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-09-02-0198-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-02-09-02-0198-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-09-02-0166-0001&amp;expandNote=GEWN-02-09-02-0166-0001-fn-0002#GEWN-02-09-02-0166-0001-fn-0002" class="document">GW to Lewis, 20 April, n.2</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-09-02-0198-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-02-09-02-0198-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p><a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-09-02-0169" class="document">Lewis sent to GW on 8</a> and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-09-02-0174" class="document">24 May</a> reports on his transactions for GW at Williamsburg.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-09-02-0198-fn-0004-ptr" id="GEWN-02-09-02-0198-fn-0004">4</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-09-02-0209" class="document">GW to James Mercer, 19 July 1773</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-09-02-0198-fn-0005-ptr" id="GEWN-02-09-02-0198-fn-0005">5</a>

   <p>Roger Dixon, a merchant in Fredericksburg, had recently died.</p>

